public enum SessionType

The SessionType of a TargetSession determines which stages can be reached in the Full Feature Phase.

Enum Constant Detail

DISCOVERY

public static final SessionType DISCOVERY
The session is a discovery session. The initiator is only allowed to issue request a list of available target and close the connection.

NORMAL

public static final SessionType NORMAL
The session is a normal session. The initiator is allowed to issue all supported commands.
